name: composite_ikab
jaxpr:
{ lambda ; a:f32[9,3]. let
    b:f32[9,3] = tanh a
    c:f32[9,3] = custom_jvp_call[
      name=relu
      call_jaxpr={ lambda ; d:f32[9,3]. let
          e:f32[9,3] = jit[
            name=relu
            jaxpr={ lambda ; d:f32[9,3]. let
                e:f32[9,3] = max d 0.0:f32[]
              in (e,) }
          ] d
        in (e,) }
      jvp=jvp
      symbolic_zeros=False
    ] a
    f:f32[9,3] = add b c
    g:f32[9,3] = sin a
    h:f32[9,3] = add f g
  in (h,) }
